					Full Description



		Bunka Shutter Co., Ltd. is a Japan-based company mainly engaged in the manufacture and sale of shutters, and housing and building materials. The Company operates in five business segments. The Shutter-related Products segment offers lightweight shutters, heavy shutters, over-sliding doors, panel shutters and window shutters. The Construction Material-related Products segment offers exterior products, cross-cut weatherboardings, doors, partitions and other related products. The Service segment offers maintenance, inspection and repair services of the Company's products. The Reform segment is engaged in the renovation of housing. The Others segment is engaged in the manufacture and sale of customized furniture, as well as the non-life insurance agency and travel agency services. It also involves in the manfuacture and sale of foundation reinforcement units, iron wires and welded wire meshes.
» Full Overview of 5930.T







