bunka shutter co ltd (5930) Details


			Bunka Shutter Co., Ltd. manufactures and sells various rolling shutters, and house and building construction materials in Japan. The company provides pole less shutters, fireproof shutters, fire and smoke proof cloth screens, air keepers, and over sliding doors for offices, factories, and warehouses; and panel and lightweight grill shutters, horizontal sliding panel shutters, smoke proof shutters and palettes, and roller awnings for shops. It also offers wooden partitions, sliding doors with automatic closing systems, toilet booths, moving partitions, lightweight steel swing and folding doors, and indoor lightweight doors for schools, houses, hospitals, and public buildings. In addition, the company provides home awnings, ventilation and lighting models, outdoor steel frame stairs and walkway units, residential over sliding doors, aluminum balconies, aluminum shutters, and hand rails for wooden frame, reinforced concrete, and steel frame constructions. Further, it offers maintenance and inspection services. The company was formerly known as Japan Bunka Shutter Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Bunka Shutter Co., Ltd. in April 1970 as a result of merger transaction with Himeji City Japan Bunka Shutter. Bunka Shutter Co., Ltd. was founded in 1955 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
  			

