PRODUCT SHUTTER | BUNKA SHUTTER CO.,LTD













 






 




 



 
 



HOME > PRODUCT SHUTTER

























































Our shutters for commercial buildings and factories are strong enough for absolute security and are designed for reliable, simple and speedy operation. Bunka Shutter have developed our shutters in response to the changing needs of industry and society. Shutters that offer protection against intruders are the one of many shutter types. We have designed shutters that serve as emergency barriers such as fire walls and smoke walls. We can cater for wide openings and provide comfortable safety in aesthetic spaces even when the shutters are closed.
Our poleless fireproof /smokeproof shutter is one example. The central pillars retract into the ceiling by folding in two, and thus creating a free space.
We are developing new shutters with flexible design approaches even for industrial shutters, which primarily are installed for air tightness, such as adding lighting windows and contributing to energy saving.


































































































































































Shutters designed for stores must meld their practical function of protection with a wide choice of attractive designs. To give the customers as free choice as possible, Bunka Shutter has created a range of products to cater for the broad range of needs. In addition to offering reliable operation and peace of mind, Bunka Shutter is working hard to enhance the design level of its products. For example, the see-through designs of "Panelook" and "Paneruler" allow stores to keep their shop window displays visible after closing. The marking film of "Palette" adds a rich expression to the streetscape while electromotive grill shutters show off the grade and the fashion of the shop.























































































































































































































































